# Linear Algebra Professor
![](https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/1158765973671780464/1162816697271603351/Untitled_Artwork-1.png?ex=653d5070&is=652adb70&hm=d64be7b433d83869cde2d3540d10d1c63308b3db0e240e9809006bc57c021caf)  
The linear algebra professor wanted students to go to lecture. The prof changed the way gravity behaves in hopes it would pull the students go to lecture.
## Eigenvectors
Eigenvectors are probably some important concept from lin alg except we all kinda forgot what they do so we're just going to say the prof used eigenvectors to warp gravity.
## Warped Gravity

The purple gas is gravity gas. If you pay close attention during the game, sometimes you will notice the jump heights vary. This is because we made thea acceleration of gravity non constant, it is now a sawtooth function ![](data:image/png;base64,)
